<plot>A man is attacked on his way home from work and falls into a parallel world where he 'lives' 6 other lives including a Rockstar, a Homeless and the very same 'hoddy' that attacked him. It transpires that he was on his way home to confess to his wife of an affair. These lives help him to re-evaluate his values and priorities and in the final chapter he is dropped off by his lover before once again confronting the hoodies in a re-enactment of the beginning of the film. However, this time the outcome will be different.....</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?006589</url></doc>
